scmRevision master
depends SlicerRT PETDICOMExtension
build_subdirectory .

homepage https://gitlab.in2p3.fr/iftim/projects/delineate
category Nuclear Medicine
iconurl https://gitlab.in2p3.fr/iftim/projects/delineate/-/raw/master/DELINEATE.png
status
description Clinical decision-support extension for nuclear medicine supporting liver tumor treatment workflows with SPECT/CT and PET/CT imaging. Provides three integrated modules: automatic AI-based liver and tumor segmentation (SegModule), multimodal image registration (RecModule), and patient-specific dosimetry computation using LDM/VDK physical models (DosiModule).
